

{"id":4380,"date":"2023-06-13T11:41:01","date_gmt":"2023-06-13T04:41:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=4380"},"modified":"2023-06-22T00:12:42","modified_gmt":"2023-06-21T17:12:42","slug":"dam-thuc-vat-hay-dam-dong-vat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/dam-thuc-vat-hay-dam-dong-vat\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt: Lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt<\/strong> hay <strong>\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/strong> &#8211; Lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp?\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt r\u1eb1ng protein l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu trong ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. C\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p protein, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, v\u00e0 do \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>Ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4573\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4573\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4573 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Chat-dam-la-gi-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4573\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn x\u01b0\u01a1ng, da v\u00e0 t\u00f3c. B\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o protein.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>T\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4563\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4563\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4563 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap-.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap-.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap--300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap--1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap--768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap--1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Tai-sao-chat-dam-lai-quan-trong-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap--2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4563\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m l\u1ea1i quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb amino acid. C\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n 22 lo\u1ea1i amino acids \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n sinh ra amino acid m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a ch\u00fang trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. V\u00ec v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m, c\u01a1 b\u1eafp c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m?<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4565\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4565\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4565 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Thuc-pham-nao-chua-dam-1-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4565\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m?<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m nh\u1ea5t, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt chi\u1ebfm 60% l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea1m ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m bao g\u1ed3m:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ecf, th\u1ecbt heo, th\u1ecbt g\u00e0, c\u00e1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ee9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ng\u0169 c\u1ed1c nguy\u00ean c\u00e1m<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eadu<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean men nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eadu h\u0169, tempeh<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #009fc2;\"><strong>\u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt l\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng amino acid m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ch\u1ee9a b\u00ean trong. \u0110\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u amino acid quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0103n m\u1ed9t h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 9 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 s\u1ea3n sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m \u201cho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;\">1. \u0110\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4571\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4571\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4571 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-dong-vat-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4571\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, ch\u00fang ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i amino acid m\u00e0 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt d\u1ec5 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, cho n\u00ean c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ec ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng amino acid cao v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u01a1 b\u1eafp.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u1ee9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb s\u1eefa (bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00f4 mai, s\u1eefa v\u00e0 whey)<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ecbt gia c\u1ea7m (th\u1ecbt g\u00e0, g\u00e0 t\u00e2y, chim c\u00fat)<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ecf (th\u1ecbt b\u00f2, th\u1ecbt nai)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;\">2. \u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4567\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4567\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4567 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/dam-thuc-vat-2048x1040.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4567\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c amino acid c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a \u00edt ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o v\u00e0 cholesterol h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c r\u1ee7i ro v\u1ec1 b\u1ec7nh tim m\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1, mang l\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ti\u00eau h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ecf qua vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe con ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i chung.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ea1t di\u00eam m\u1ea1ch<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u00faa m\u1ea1ch \u0111en<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ea1t c\u00e2y gai d\u1ea7u<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u1ea1t chia<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1eadu n\u00e0nh<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u01a1m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #333333;\">3. \u0110\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt vs \u0110\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt: Lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp?<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4569\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4569\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4569 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/loai-nao-toi-uu-hon-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap.png\" alt=\"\u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt, \u0111\u1ea1m th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt hay \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1m\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/loai-nao-toi-uu-hon-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap.png 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/loai-nao-toi-uu-hon-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/loai-nao-toi-uu-hon-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/loai-nao-toi-uu-hon-trong-viec-xay-dung-co-bap-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-conte